{
  "id": "adv_card_ngs_11_03",
  "title": "伊吹渚 3話 まだ満足してません",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――撮影終わりの帰り道",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― On the way home after filming",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（連日撮影が続く中、渚は役のモデルが自分だと）\n（知ってから、さらに演技に磨きがかかっていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（With filming continuing for days‚ Nagisa found out）\n（the model for her role was herself‚ and her acting improved further）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（一応最後の撮影まで付き添う予定だが、明日は）\n（芽衣の撮影もあるんだよな。時間は大丈夫だったか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I plan to accompany her until the final shoot‚ but tomorrow）\n（there's also Mei's shoot. Was the timing okay…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 18.8897504967
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "今、私以外の子のこと考えてました？\n私が隣にいるのに……酷い……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Were you just thinking about someone else besides me?\nEven though I'm right here next to you… How cruel…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　あ、い、いや……\n一応、スケジュールの確認を、と思っただけで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!? A-Ah‚ no…\nI was just trying to check the schedule‚ for now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 33.5028790315
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、ごめんなさい、深い意味はなくて……\nだ、ダメですね、どうも最近役が抜けなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ sorry‚ I didn't mean anything deep by that…\nI-I can't help it‚ I just haven't been able to shake off the role lately…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんだそういうことだったのか……\nびっくりしたぞ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-What‚ so that's what it was…\nYou really surprised me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.0739990119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――さらに数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― A few more days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.5304294269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.0637628396
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.0637628396
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "今日の演技、どうでしたか？\nちゃんと見守ってくれていましたよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How was my acting today?\nYou were watching over me properly‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "も……もちろん、ちゃんと見ていたよ\n誰にも文句を言わせない素晴らしい演技だったぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-Of course‚ I was watching closely.\nIt was a brilliant performance that no one could complain about.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.9405649186
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "良かった……{user}さんのおかげです\n貴方がそばでずっと見てくれているから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank goodness… It's all thanks to you‚ {user}.\nBecause you're always by my side watching me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.9704517366
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "だからずっと私のこと見守っていて下さいね\n約束ですよ？　破らないで下さいね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So please‚ keep watching over me.\nIt's a promise‚ okay? Don't break it‚ alright?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.0149179143
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（ライバル役のアリサちゃんが憑依してるぞ……渚……）\n（だが下手に突っ込んで演技に影響が出たら問題だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She's possessed by Arisa‚ the rival character… Nagisa…）\n（But it'll be a problem if I point it out and it affects her acting）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（撮影が終わるまではこのままにしておこう……）\n（生きた心地がしないが）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I'll leave it like this until the filming is over…）\n（Though I feel like I'm barely holding on）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.0666656494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――渚の最終撮影日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― Nagisa's final day of filming",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.8206761044,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.5206761838
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.5206761838
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（今日でついに渚のクランクアップ……）\n（主人公達の結婚式に飛び込んでくるシーンだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Today is finally Nagisa's crank-up…）\n（It's the scene where she crashes the main characters' wedding）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.9764097881,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.4623375258
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 104.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "おかしいよ、今日は私とコウタ君の結婚式でしょう！？\nどうしてその女と結ばれようとしてるのっ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's strange‚ today was supposed to be mine and Kota's wedding‚ right!?\nWhy are you trying to be with that woman!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.7999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.1229724886
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ、どうしてっ、なんで！！\n貴方を幸せに出来るのは……！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tell me‚ why‚ why!!\nThe one who can make you happy is…!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.9999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "わ……私じゃ、なかったの……？\nユイナじゃないと、ダメ、なの……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wasn't it… me…?\nDoes it have to be Yuina…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.5333323161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.6891403518
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "ぐすっ……分かっ、分かってたよ……ずっと！\nそんなの分かってた！！　だってコウタ君のこと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sob… I-I knew it… all along!\nI knew that!! But‚ because I… Kota…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.6999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "私、なんでも知ってるもん……大好き、だから……\n幸せになってね……絶対だよ？　結婚、おめでとう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know everything about you… because I love you…\nYou have to be happy… promise me? Congratulations on your wedding…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.2999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.1296153708
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（渚が……ライバル役も素敵なキャラだと言った理由）\n（この台詞でなんとなく分かった気がするな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The reason Nagisa said the rival was also a wonderful character）\n（I feel like I understand now from these lines…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 172.5551345829
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "最後のシーンも一発OK、ですか……？\nあ、ありがとうございますっ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Was the last scene a one-take OK too…?\nAh‚ thank you so much!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.4333414714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "本当に凄い演技だったぞ、渚……\nそばで最後まで見れて良かったよ……ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was truly amazing acting‚ Nagisa…\nI'm glad I could watch you until the end… Thank you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.6333414714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_wedding-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "wedding-00-noon",
      "startTime": 186.5217338566
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_03-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "お礼を言うのは私の方です\nずっと付き合ってくれてありがとうございました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm the one who should be thanking you\nThank you for staying with me the whole time!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.4666748047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
